---
title: Plant-Based Mince & Mushroom Fusilli with Parmesan Cheese & Parsley
description: It’s our favourite night again, pasta night! Twirly fusilli is the perfect shape to capture saucy veggie mince and tender veggies, making every a bite a balancing act of savoury flavours.

